                                ; """
                                ;   Simple ballistic Rocket launch
                                ;   without air resistance
                                ; """
                                ; Modified Jun 26 2026 to do several graphics refresh cycles in between each velocity
                                ; calculation; net result is that the length of wall-clock time to complete the flight
                                ; can be adjusted to taste.
                                ;  The Murrow film takes over 20 seconds to complete the flight; with no artificial delay,
                                ; this program completes a cycle in less than two seconds, making it hard to see what's happening
                                ; with the gauges.
                                ;  Pacing can be adjusted by changing the small negative number in "delay_init"
                                ;

                                .dbwgt c_fuel, 0o400

                                .org 0
